summary: I WENT TO LEAVE IN MY CAR AND IT WOULDNT START, THE CAR PUT ITS SELF IN NEUTRAL  AND WOULD NOT MOVE. THE EMERGENCY BREAK LIGHT CAME ON AND THE ENGINE LIGHT CAME ON. CAR STILL WOULDN'T START. AFTER 3 HOURS THE CAR STARTES AND WAS BACK IN PARK. THE ENGINE AND PARKING LIGHT WAS AND STILL IS ON. THERE HAS BEEN RECALLS ON 2015 CHRYSLER 200'S FOR THIS ISSUE.  BUT NOT MINE!!!!
